com.camerontec.catalys.server.compliance

Class ComplianceFilterSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.server.compliance.ComplianceFilter
      • com.camerontec.catalys.server.compliance.ValidityFilter
        • com.camerontec.catalys.server.compliance.ComplianceFilterSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IComplianceFilter, IFilterContainer, IConfigurableContainer

    public class ComplianceFilterSet
extends ValidityFilter
implements IFilterContainer
    ComplianceFilterSet is a compliance filter that is responsible for checking basic message validity, populating the context and then applying all enabled filters. No validity checks are performed until it is certain that a filter needs to be validated.
    Author:
    Tom Vasak
